# Predicting-Liver-Cirrhosis-Using-Advanced-Machine-Learning-Techniques
# Liver Cirrhosis ML Project

A machine learning project to predict patient survival outcomes using the Liver Cirrhosis dataset from UCI Machine Learning Repository.

---

## 📊 Dataset

- Source: UCI Machine Learning Repository
- Dataset: [Liver Cirrhosis Patient Data](https://archive.ics.uci.edu/dataset/597/liver+cirrhosis)

This dataset includes patient information like bilirubin levels, albumin, age, and other features to predict survival outcomes.

---

## 💡 Objective

To train a classification model to predict whether a patient will **live or die**, based on medical parameters.

